cast.overview: The career of screenwriter Dalton Trumbo is halted by a witch hunt in the late 1940s when he defies the anti-communist HUAC committee and is blacklisted.
cast.title: Trumbo

details.biography:
Laura Flannery is a Los Angeles based SAG AFTRA actress. Born in New Orleans, La. Laura began her acting career at Story Land in City Park, New Orleans and then a children's theater group called Summer Stages. Looking to expand beyond the stage, she signed with a talent agent at 13 years of age and took on-screen acting classes. A week later she booked her first principal role in a national commercial.

Known for Americal Horror Story: Freak Show, Astronaut Wives Club, Tattooed Love and Exit 14.
details.name: Laura Flannery
